name: DilliVideos

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dilli videos
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill allows users with display enabled Alexa devices such as Echo Show to play public videos uploaded to Dilli Videos at http://videos.dillilabs.com. Give it a try, say "Play a Video" to play a random video or say "Play a video on handball" to play a random video about the sports of handball. 

Upload videos on Dilli Videos, tag them and watch them via Dilli Videos Alexa skill by simply saying "Play a video on <tag>". Perfect for celebrities and content publishers to generate a fan following on Alexa devices. For more information contact us at info@dillilbs.com.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
